{"tid":211544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（胃癌支國）全球新增胃癌病例，一半在支那！","createTime":"2017-04-21T16:45:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T16:51:11.000Z","uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6a062e27c1aae0caf17588f5a683861430b76828","tid":211544,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:45:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170421/photo/bkncn-20170421181421565-0421_05011_001_01p.jpg?20170421191845\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170421%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170421181421565-0421_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20170421191845&h=72419703&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\n<br />\n\r<br />\n第12屆國際胃癌大會昨日在北京開幕，&hellip;&hellip;。會上公布的數據顯示，中國每年新增的胃癌病例約為68萬宗，佔全球發病病例一半左右，大部分患者診斷時已為中晚期。<br />\r\n<br />\n\r<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n\r<br />\n由於胃癌一經發現常為中晚期，患者存活超過5年的機會一般低於30%；<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;不健康的生活飲食習慣是胃癌發生的重要危險因素；胃癌患者中，30至40歲的患者並不罕見，大都是抽煙成癮、嗜酒如命、愛吃油炸熱燙食物、三餐不定時、少吃蔬菜水果、工作壓力大、缺乏運動等。"},{"pid":"4512ba879d98a9d67d895391e478ab1aeff6edec","tid":211544,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:49:19.000Z","msg":"坑渠油唔提？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19247f750bf17185a1689ba36f1a04bfb4d2a6be","tid":211544,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:51:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>坑渠油唔提？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有中國特色既土產黎"}]}